data.description: **Seller offering $5,000 towards closing costs/rate buy down** Welcome to this exclusive retreat located in the heart of Southshore, minutes to Us Hwy 301, I-75 and major retail and dining. With 5 Bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a 3 car garage and a NEW ROOF (2023) you can enjoy everything that suburban living has to offer in this spacious home with several flex spaces and lots of possibilities. Features fresh exterior paint, hard wood flooring on the main level, built-in desk and cabinets in office, large family room, downstairs bedroom and full bathroom perfect for guests, a key drop area conveniently located just beside the garage door, large loft area, large bedrooms all with walk-in closets, a water softener and a 3 car tandem garage. The kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, including a new microwave and range, granite counters, 42" staggered upper cabinets w/crown molding, island with room for bar stools, and large corner closet pantry. The master suite is a sanctuary with his and hers walk-in closets, dual split granite vanities, a garden tub and separate shower, and direct access to the laundry room featuring Closets by Design built in cabinetry. Enjoy the Florida lifestyle from the covered patio overlooking a lovely yard. Other features include recessed lighting, 3 car tandem garage, inviting covered front porch and much more. The Oaks at Shady Creek community shares a vibrant lifestyle with a clubhouse, community pool, playground and basketball court. Ready for immediate move in, this won't last long. View our 3D virtual tour and call for your personal tour today!
